---
// Experience Section Component
---

<section id="experiencia" class="experience-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title" data-translate="experience-title">
        Experiencia
      </h2>
      <p class="section-description" data-translate="experience-desc">
        Mi trayectoria profesional y laboral
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="experience-timeline">
      <!-- NTT DATA – grouped card with two roles -->
      <div class="experience-card experience-card--group">

        <!-- Company header (shared) -->
        <div class="group-company-header">
          <div class="company-logo">
            <img
              src="/images/nttdataImagen.webp"
              alt="NTT DATA Logo"
              data-translate="ntt-logo-alt"
              class="logo-img"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="group-company-meta">
            <span class="group-company-name" data-translate="ntt-company-name">NTT DATA</span>
            <span class="group-company-total" data-translate="ntt-total-period">nov. 2025 - actualidad</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Internal timeline -->
        <div class="internal-timeline">

          <!-- Role 1: Junior Engineer (current) -->
          <div class="internal-role">
            <div class="role-connector">
              <div class="role-dot role-dot--current"></div>
              <div class="role-line"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="role-body">
              <div class="role-header">
                <h3 class="role-title" data-translate="ntt-junior-role">Ingeniero Junior</h3>
                <span class="role-badge role-badge--current" data-translate="ntt-current-badge">Actual</span>
              </div>
              <div class="role-contract" data-translate="ntt-junior-contract">NTT DATA · Contrato indefinido</div>
              <div class="period-location">
                <span class="period" data-translate="ntt-junior-period">abr. 2026 - actualidad</span>
                <span class="separator">•</span>
                <span class="location" data-translate="ntt-location">La Coruña, Galicia, España · Híbrido</span>
              </div>
              <p class="description" data-translate="ntt-junior-desc">
                Tras mi promoción a Ingeniero Junior, me incorporé a un nuevo proyecto con un stack backend similar (Java, Spring, Hibernate, Oracle y Docker), asumiendo mayor responsabilidad técnica. Participo de forma end-to-end en el análisis, diseño e implementación de evolutivos e incidencias, colaborando estrechamente con perfiles técnicos y funcionales en un entorno ágil.
              </p>
              <div class="tags-container">
                <span class="tech-tag">Java</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Spring</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Hibernate</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Oracle</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Docker</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Maven</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Git</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Role 2: Student (completed) -->
          <div class="internal-role">
            <div class="role-connector">
              <div class="role-dot role-dot--past"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="role-body">
              <div class="role-header">
                <h3 class="role-title role-title--past" data-translate="ntt-role">Estudiante en prácticas</h3>
              </div>
              <div class="role-contract" data-translate="ntt-company-contract">NTT DATA · Contrato de prácticas</div>
              <div class="period-location">
                <span class="period" data-translate="ntt-period">nov. 2025 - mar. 2026</span>
                <span class="separator">•</span>
                <span class="location" data-translate="ntt-location">La Coruña, Galicia, España · Híbrido</span>
              </div>
              <p class="description" data-translate="ntt-desc">
                Durante mi etapa de prácticas participé en dos proyectos distintos relacionados con el índice sanitario, con una base tecnológica similar pero enfoques diferentes: uno sobre una arquitectura más consolidada y otro sobre un entorno más moderno y actualizado.
                <br /><br />
                En ambos contribuí al análisis técnico, desarrollo de nuevas funcionalidades y resolución de incidencias, reforzando la calidad del software mediante pruebas, revisión de código y documentación técnica en metodología ágil.
              </p>
              <div class="tags-container">
                <span class="tech-tag">Java</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Spring</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Hibernate</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">PHP</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Oracle</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Docker</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">HL7</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Mirth Connect</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Maven</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Git</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">JIRA</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Confluence</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">IntelliJ IDEA</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div><!-- /internal-timeline -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .experience-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e1b4b 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .experience-section::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background-image: radial-gradient(
        circle at 10% 20%,
        rgba(0, 245, 255, 0.08) 0%,
        transparent 40%
      ),
      radial-gradient(
        circle at 90% 80%,
        rgba(217, 70, 239, 0.08) 0%,
        transparent 40%
      ),
      linear-gradient(
        0deg,
        transparent 0%,
        rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02) 50%,
        transparent 100%
      );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      var(--accent-cyan),
      var(--accent-purple)
    );
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .section-description {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .experience-timeline {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Specificity boost with ID */
  #experiencia .experience-card {
    background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.4);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  #experiencia .experience-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.6);
  }

  .card-header {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .company-logo-wrapper {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .company-logo {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    min-width: 80px;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .logo-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    display: block;
  }

  .header-info {
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .role-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .company-name {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .period-location {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .separator {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .card-body .description {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .tags-container {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .tech-tag {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .tech-tag:hover {
    background: rgba(0, 245, 255, 0.1);
    border-color: var(--accent-cyan);
    color: #fff;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .card-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
  }

  /* Light Mode Styles */
  html.light-mode .experience-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff 0%, #dbeafe 100%);
  }

  html.light-mode .experience-section::before {
    background-image: radial-gradient(
        circle at 10% 20%,
        rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.08) 0%,
        transparent 40%
      ),
      radial-gradient(
        circle at 90% 80%,
        rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.08) 0%,
        transparent 40%
      );
  }

  html.light-mode .section-title {
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      var(--accent-blue),
      var(--accent-purple)
    );
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  html.light-mode #experiencia .experience-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  html.light-mode #experiencia .experience-card:hover {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-color: var(--accent-blue);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.15);
  }

  html.light-mode .role-title {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  html.light-mode .company-name {
    color: var(--accent-blue);
  }

  html.light-mode .period-location {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  html.light-mode .card-body .description {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  html.light-mode .tech-tag {
    background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.05);
    border-color: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2);
    color: var(--accent-blue);
  }

  html.light-mode .tech-tag:hover {
    background: var(--accent-blue);
    color: #fff;
  }

  /* ── Grouped card ─────────────────────────────────────── */
  .experience-card--group {
    padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
  }

  .group-company-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }

  .group-company-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
  }

  .group-company-name {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .group-company-total {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  /* ── Internal timeline ─────────────────────────────────── */
  .internal-timeline {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .internal-role {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .role-connector {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 18px;
    padding-top: 4px;
  }

  .role-dot {
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .role-dot--current {
    background: var(--accent-cyan);
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 245, 255, 0.5);
  }

  .role-dot--past {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  }

  .role-line {
    flex-grow: 1;
    width: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0, 245, 255, 0.4), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06));
    margin: 5px 0;
  }

  .role-body {
    flex-grow: 1;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .internal-role:last-child .role-body {
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .role-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .role-title {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .role-title--past {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .role-badge {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 2rem;
  }

  .role-badge--current {
    background: rgba(0, 245, 255, 0.12);
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 245, 255, 0.3);
  }

  .role-contract {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .role-body .description {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0.75rem 0 1.25rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  /* ── Light mode overrides ──────────────────────────────── */
  html.light-mode .group-company-header {
    border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07);
  }

  html.light-mode .role-dot--current {
    background: var(--accent-blue);
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.4);
  }

  html.light-mode .role-dot--past {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
  }

  html.light-mode .role-line {
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.35), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05));
  }

  html.light-mode .role-title--past {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  html.light-mode .role-badge--current {
    background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);
    color: var(--accent-blue);
    border-color: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.25);
  }

  html.light-mode .role-contract {
    color: var(--accent-blue);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .experience-card--group {
      padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
